Title: Coupling supergravity to non-supersymmetric matter
Author: J\"{o}rg Teschner
Comments: 11 pages, LATEX, references added
Report-no: LPTHE 96-12
Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B390 (1997) 172-178
\\
  By introducing a nonlinearly transforming goldstino field
non-super\-sym\-metric matter can be coupled to supergravity. This implies the
possibility of coupling a standard model with one Higgs to supergravity.
